{"tid":2060390,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭一年喇  送頭師有幾句想講講","createTime":"2020-06-11T15:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T06:55:50.000Z","uid":168609,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3bff5bbb0b4e9d3c473468e3d609586fc8ff7c","tid":2060390,"uid":168609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:07:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">首先，想多謝一直仲堅持緊嘅手足<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（俾啲掌聲自己先啦）</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n講真，而家仲肯出嚟嘅其實都有定心理準備被咬。。。<br />\n<br />\n作為有些少經驗嘅送頭師，有三個point想大家嚟緊行街嘅時候記住：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>（1）諗清楚自己做緊乜，做嘅嘢有無意義</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n         講到口都臭啦，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">唔好漫無目的行行企企</span></span>。如果無嘢做嘅話，就返屋企打文宣戰同國際戰線。不要9fing ~ <span style=\"color: orange;\">特別係當條街開始少街坊</span>（就講六月九號，啲狗都係等到啲放工人潮走晒先發癲鳩射亂咬）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>（2）時刻留意包圍網，不被捕先係重點</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n         無容置疑，黑警嘅包圍網戰術已經練到爐火純青（母親節同五月廿七就係最好例子）。除咗<span style=\"font-size: large;\">睇哨頻</span>之外，建議大家set個alarm定時提自己諗下，身處嘅地方<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">有無多於一條嘅逃生路線</span></span>。最重要，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">睇熟地圖睇熟地圖睇熟地圖</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>（3）唔好帶無謂嘢，淨係帶必須嘢</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n         喺鄧小強帶領下，狗隊嘅戰略已經完全改變：盡量減少對峙，彈藥可免則免；同時加重人手，stop&amp;search有殺錯無放過。<span style=\"color: blue;\">出得嚟嘅手足，真係要預咗會被ss，不要心存僥倖</span>。黑警係唔會同你講法律／道理的 - 因為佢哋唔識。<br />\n<br />\n以上都係老生常談，唔係咩真知灼見。但都照打出嚟，可以救到一個手足我都已經心滿意足。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">最後想講，同手足們抗爭，我很快樂。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7246f4850ca25ff7165df4b99fa7c35f5eaf1b9","tid":2060390,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:08:01.000Z","msg":"中共咁大個春袋唔係唔錫呀嘛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"76ecd0fac9d0fa37736c46cc316cbbcc9f469c99","tid":2060390,"uid":245711,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:09:20.000Z","msg":"手足 點解要叫自己做送頭師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90782774a7a54aefff056b2c6fe2912b92f2ebb5","tid":2060390,"uid":168609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:09:28.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"cfa31ce20af6dec6125fcceae06e2710bed2c964","tid":2060390,"uid":168609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"894a17768122fe880ce53dfd44030e0c72a94aa4","tid":2060390,"uid":168609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:10:31.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"55d61aa105dba9f482843c6151b08546d77a8d39","tid":2060390,"uid":168609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"b1ece3627e47419b076bb8f9e31976f6708a4fcf","tid":2060390,"uid":99356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:12:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"403ba9614df561d54e3178a6b0d43904711603bd","tid":2060390,"uid":99356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:12:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4edf7d6a9a2f44e3dda3ae15fbafa5f3c9f7b3c2","tid":2060390,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"其實真係老生常談"},{"pid":"d949d87d21399f4e1f69450a3ee18a7486f4e92